<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">عَنْ عَبْدِ اللَّهِ قالَ:</span> قالَ النَّبِيُّ <span class="special">ﷺ</span>:<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c2">«أَوَّلُ مَا يُقْضَى بَيْنَ النَّاسِ فِي الدِّمَاءِ»</span>.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>